<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.9.7">
<l>teriyēṉ pālakaṉāyp palatīmaikaḷ ceytumiṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>periyē ṉāyiṉapiṉ piṟarkkēyuḻait tēḻaiyāṉēṉ</l>
<l>karicērp pūmpoḻilcūḻ kaṉamāmalai vēṅkaṭavā</l>
<l>variyē vantaṭaintē ṉaṭiyēṉaiyāṭ koṇṭaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As a boy who did not know [better],</l>
<l rend="indent">I also ultimately committed many wrongs.</l>
<l>After I became bigger, I became a wretch, toiling for others.</l>
<l>You of Vēṅkaṭa, the great broad mountain</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by flowering groves with elephants,</l>
<l>[My] lion, I came [here] and took refuge;</l>
<l rend="indent">be gracious, receiving me, your servant, in service.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
